          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4173251/pexels-photo-4173251.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200" alt="Medical professional in white coat reviewing patient records" width="1200" height="1500" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/1200x1500/0A0E1A/E8EEFF/png?text=Medical+Professionals';">
