      <a class="profession-card" href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/medical-professionals/osteopathic-physicians/">
        <div class="profession-num">07</div>
        <h3 class="profession-title">Osteopathic Physicians (DOs)</h3>
        <p class="profession-tag">DOs with full MD scope post-2020 ACGME merger. OMM/NMM specialty unique to DOs. ABMS + AOA dual-board pathways. Multi-source W-2 + S-corp K-1 + IBR/IDR.</p>
        <ul class="profession-points">
          <li>Full MD scope post-2020 merger</li>
