      </a>

      <a class="profession-card" href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/medical-professionals/anesthesiologists/">
        <div class="profession-num">08</div>
        <h3 class="profession-title">Anesthesiologists</h3>
        <p class="profession-tag">Hospital-employed + ASC equity multi-entity + locum multi-state. ABA + ASA + fellowship subspecialties. W-2 + K-1 with multi-entity Form 1084.</p>
        <ul class="profession-points">
          <li>ABA + ASA + fellowship subspec</li>
          <li>ASC equity multi-entity</li>
