        </ul>
        <span class="profession-link">Read the anesthesiologist mortgage guide</span>
      </a>

      <a class="profession-card" href="https://stairwaymortgage.com/medical-professionals/nurse-anesthetists/">
        <div class="profession-num">09</div>
        <h3 class="profession-title">Nurse Anesthetists (CRNAs)</h3>
        <p class="profession-tag">CRNAs with DNP-by-2025 mandate. NBCRNA + AANA + COA. Hospital + CRNA-only groups + locum + subspecialty (dental/GI/plastic surgery/OB).</p>
        <ul class="profession-points">
          <li>DNP-by-2025 mandate</li>
